  <description><![CDATA[<p>A warm welcome is provided by the team at the Hotel Sonnschein. The hotel has room types to suit everyone and leisure facilities including two indoor pools.</p>
<h2>Rooms</h2>
<p>The hotel has a relaxed and informal atmosphere. The main hotel building is the original building, which houses the reception, dining room and some guest bedrooms. Two newer wings are connected to the main building, one is decorated in a traditional Tyrolean style and the other has a more modern style.</p>
<p>Ideal for families, with a variety of room types including spacious family rooms. There is also a great variety of twin and single rooms available.</p>
<h2>Wellness World</h2>
<p>The Hotel Sonnschein has upgraded their leisure facilities for this winter which includes two swimming pools and plenty of places to relax.</p>
<p>Chill out in the family area with indoor pool with whirlpool corner, or head to the adults only area with a Mediterranean indoor pool with underwater massage loungers. The adults only spa area also has infrared cabin, multiple saunas and steam rooms and a waterfall room.</p>
<h2>Facilities</h2>
<p>If you are looking for somewhere to relax after a day on the slopes, head to the game room with table tennis and pool table. There is also a children's playroom for the little ones.</p>]]></description>
